            heading: 'Things You Should Know Before Going',
            headingZh: '出发前须知',
            blocks: [
              { type: 'subheading', num: '1', text: 'It is not completely effortless', zh: '并非完全轻松' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'While I would not consider this a difficult hike, it is <strong class="hl">not a casual walk</strong> either.', zh: '虽然我不认为这是一条困难的路线，但它也<strong class="hl">绝非随意的散步</strong>。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'People who rarely exercise may find certain sections challenging, especially the <strong class="hl">steeper climbs near the beginning</strong> of the route.', zh: '对于平时很少运动的人来说，某些路段可能会有挑战性，尤其是<strong class="hl">路线初段较为陡峭的上坡</strong>部分。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'If you hike occasionally and have a reasonable fitness level, however, the trail should be <strong class="hl">very manageable</strong>.', zh: '但如果你偶尔徒步、体力尚可，这条路线应该<strong class="hl">完全可以胜任</strong>。' },

              { type: 'subheading', num: '2', text: 'There is almost no shade', zh: '几乎没有遮荫处' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'This is an <strong class="hl">exposed ridge hike</strong>.', zh: '这是一条<strong class="hl">暴露的山脊路线</strong>。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'There are very few trees along the route, meaning <strong class="hl">almost no protection from the sun</strong>.', zh: '沿途几乎没有树木，意味着<strong class="hl">几乎没有任何遮蔽阳光的地方</strong>。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'On warm summer days, especially around noon and in the afternoon, the heat can feel <strong class="hl">surprisingly intense</strong>.', zh: '在温暖的夏日，尤其是正午前后，阳光直射可能<strong class="hl">出乎意料地强烈</strong>。' },
              { type: 'ul', intro: 'I strongly recommend:', items: [
                '<strong class="hl">Bringing sufficient water</strong>',
                'Using sunscreen',
                'Wearing a hat or cap',
                '<strong class="hl">Starting early</strong> whenever possible',
              ], zhIntro: '我强烈建议：', zhItems: [
                '<strong class="hl">携带充足的饮用水</strong>',
                '涂抹防晒霜',
                '佩戴帽子或遮阳帽',
                '尽可能<strong class="hl">早出发</strong>',
              ]},

              { type: 'subheading', num: '3', text: 'No facilities on the ridge', zh: '山脊上没有任何设施' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'Once you leave the stations, there are:', zh: '一旦离开站点，沿途将没有：' },
