                '<strong class="hl">无厕所</strong>',
                '<strong class="hl">无餐饮摊点</strong>',
                '<strong class="hl">无饮用水补给点</strong>',
              ]},
              { type: 'p', text: 'Make sure you <strong class="hl">bring everything you need</strong> before starting.', zh: '请务必在出发前<strong class="hl">备齐所有所需物品</strong>。' },

              { type: 'subheading', num: '4', text: 'Wear proper footwear', zh: '请穿着合适的鞋履' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'You do not need heavy mountaineering boots for this trail.', zh: '这条路线不需要专业登山靴。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'A good pair of <strong class="hl">hiking shoes or sturdy sports shoes</strong> is usually sufficient.', zh: '一双优质的<strong class="hl">徒步鞋或结实的运动鞋</strong>通常已经足够。' },
              { type: 'ul', intro: 'However, I would avoid:', items: ['Sandals', 'Casual fashion shoes', 'Leather dress shoes'],
                zhIntro: '但建议避免穿：', zhItems: ['凉鞋', '休闲便鞋', '皮革正装鞋'] },
              { type: 'p', text: 'The trail includes <strong class="hl">uneven terrain where proper grip is important</strong>.', zh: '路线涉及不平整的地形，<strong class="hl">合适的鞋底抓地力非常重要</strong>。' },

              { type: 'subheading', num: '5', text: 'Hiking poles are helpful — but not always', zh: '登山杖有帮助，但并非随时都适用' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'I highly recommend hiking poles, especially for the steeper sections.', zh: '我强烈推荐使用登山杖，尤其是在较陡的路段。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'They can <strong class="hl">save a significant amount of energy</strong> during climbs and <strong class="hl">reduce stress on your knees</strong> during descents.', zh: '登山杖能在上坡时<strong class="hl">节省大量体力</strong>，并在下坡时<strong class="hl">减轻膝关节的负担</strong>。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'That said, Stoos Ridge is a very popular route. During busy periods, some sections can become crowded.', zh: '不过，Stoos 山脊是一条非常热门的路线，旺季某些路段可能相当拥挤。' },
              { type: 'p', text: "On flatter and narrower stretches, I usually put my poles away to avoid slowing down other hikers or accidentally getting in someone's way.", zh: '在较平坦或较窄的路段，我通常会收起登山杖，以免妨碍其他徒步者。' },
            ],
          },
          {
            heading: 'Safety',
            headingZh: '安全注意事项',
            blocks: [
              { type: 'p', text: 'Although I personally consider the overall risk level relatively low, it is <strong class="hl">still a mountain ridge</strong>.', zh: '尽管我个人认为整体风险水平相对较低，但这<strong class="hl">毕竟是一条山脊路线</strong>。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'The views are spectacular and it is easy to become distracted while taking photos.', zh: '沿途风景令人叹为观止，很容易在拍照时分散注意力。' },
              { type: 'p', text: '<strong class="hl">Always pay attention to where you are stepping</strong>, particularly when stopping for pictures or looking away from the trail.', zh: '<strong class="hl">请始终注意脚下</strong>，尤其是在停下来拍照或视线离开路面时。' },
              { type: 'p', text: '<strong class="hl">No photograph is worth an injury.</strong>', zh: '<strong class="hl">没有任何一张照片值得以受伤为代价。</strong>' },
            ],
