            heading: 'Getting There',
            headingZh: '交通与前往方式',
            blocks: [
              { type: 'p', text: 'Another highlight of this trip is the journey itself.', zh: '这次旅程的另一大亮点是前往途中的体验本身。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'Before reaching the ridge, you can ride the famous Stoos funicular, which is often described as <strong class="hl">the steepest funicular railway in the world</strong>.', zh: '在抵达山脊之前，你可以乘坐著名的 Stoos 缆车——这条缆车常被描述为<strong class="hl">世界上坡度最陡的缆车</strong>。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'From Stoos village, you can then take the chairlift up to Klingenstock and begin the hike.', zh: '从 Stoos 村，可再乘坐椅式吊椅上行至 Klingenstock，然后开始徒步。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'Transport schedules may change depending on the season, weather conditions, and maintenance work, so I recommend <strong class="hl">checking the <a href="https://www.stoos.ch/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px">official Stoos website</a> before departure</strong>.', zh: '交通时刻表可能因季节、天气和维护工作而有所变化，建议<strong class="hl">出发前查阅 <a href="https://www.stoos.ch/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px">Stoos 官方网站</a></strong>。' },
