              { type: 'p', text: 'It offers an <strong class="hl">ideal balance between spectacular scenery, reasonable effort, and accessibility</strong>. Whether you are visiting Switzerland for the first time or have lived here for years, it is a route that <strong class="hl">deserves a place on your hiking list</strong>.', zh: '它在<strong class="hl">壮观的风景、适中的体力要求和便利的交通之间找到了理想的平衡</strong>。无论你是第一次来到瑞士，还是在这里生活多年，它都是一条<strong class="hl">值得列入徒步清单</strong>的路线。' },
              { type: 'p', text: 'If you have already completed the hike, or if you are planning to visit soon, feel free to leave a comment and share your experience.', zh: '如果你已经走过这条路线，或者正在计划近期前往，欢迎在下方留言分享你的体验。' },
