      heroIntro: [
        'Oeschinensee was not a spontaneous destination for me.',
        'Like many hikers, I had seen countless photographs of its famous turquoise water long before my visit. In fact, I was so excited about the trip that I painted my nails in a shade that closely matched the colour of the lake before leaving home. Completely unnecessary, of course — but probably a good indication of how much I had been looking forward to this.',
